n your rage! Behold, God has full knowledge of what is in the hearts [of men]!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/412.mp3","surahId":3,"words":[{"id":76247,"position":1,"arabic":"هَـٰٓأَنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরাই তো","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76248,"position":2,"arabic":"أُو۟لَآءِ","translation":"ঐসব লোক","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76249,"position":3,"arabic":"تُحِبُّونَهُمْ","translation":"তাদেরকে ভালবাস","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76250,"position":4,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"অথচ না","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76251,"position":5,"arabic":"يُحِبُّونَكُمْ","translation":"তোমাদেরকে তারা ভালবাসে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76252,"position":6,"arabic":"وَتُؤْمِنُونَ","translation":"এবং তোমরা বিশ্বাস কর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76253,"position":7,"arabic":"بِٱلْكِتَـٰبِ","translation":"কিতাবের উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76254,"position":8,"arabic":"كُلِّهِۦ","translation":"সবগুলোর","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76255,"position":9,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","translation":"এবং যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76256,"position":10,"arabic":"لَقُوكُمْ","translation":"তারা তোমাদের সাথে সাক্ষাৎ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76257,"position":11,"arabic":"قَالُوٓا۟","translation":"তারা বলে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76258,"position":12,"arabic":"ءَامَنَّا","translation":"''আমরাও ঈমান এনেছি''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76259,"position":13,"arabic":"وَإِذَا","translation":"আর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76260,"position":14,"arabic":"خَلَوْا۟","translation":"তারা একান্তে মিলে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76261,"position":15,"arabic":"عَضُّوا۟","translation":"তারা কামড়ায়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76262,"position":16,"arabic":"عَلَيْكُمُ","translation":"তোমাদের বিরুদ্ধে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76263,"position":17,"arabic":"ٱلْأَنَامِلَ","translation":"(তাদের) আঙ্গুলগুলোকে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76264,"position":18,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"কারণে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76265,"position":19,"arabic":"ٱلْغَيْظِ ۚ","translation":"আক্রোশের","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76267,"position":20,"arabic":"قُلْ","translation":"বলো","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76268,"position":21,"arabic":"مُوتُوا۟","translation":"তোমরা মরো","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76269,"position":22,"arabic":"بِغَيْظِكُمْ ۗ","translation":"তোমাদের আক্রোশে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76271,"position":23,"arabic":"إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76272,"position":24,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76273,"position":25,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌۢ","translation":"অধিক অবহিত","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76274,"position":26,"arabic":"بِذَاتِ","translation":"অবস্থা সম্পর্কে","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76275,"position":27,"arabic":"ٱلصُّدُورِ","translation":"(তোমাদের) বুকের (অর্থাৎ অন্তরের)''","audioUrl":"wbw/003_119_029.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":76276,"position":28,"arabic":"١١٩","translation":"(১১৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":120,"arabic":"إِن تَمْسَسْكُمْ حَسَنَةٌۭ تَسُؤْهُمْ وَإِن تُصِبْكُمْ سَيِّئَةٌۭ يَفْرَحُوا۟ بِهَا ۖ وَإِن تَصْبِرُوا۟ وَتَتَّقُوا۟ لَا ي